description: Empower Clinics Inc., an integrated healthcare company, provides body and mind wellness services for patients through digital and telemedicine care, and medical diagnostics laboratories in the United States and Canada. The company operates a pipeline of 33 clinics in Alberta, British Columbia, and New Brunswick. It has a strategic alliance with SoLVBL Solutions Inc. to develop a program for data security in diagnostic testing. Empower Clinics Inc. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
